Map created by Whisky.

Includes:
a few costum textures, 40 spawns (20 per team), cubemaps, 
alot of space to walk, teleports and a secret music xD

You dont need to put any files other than the map in your cstrike folder, the materials +
music are included inside the bsp map file.
